00:00:40.340 --> 00:00:41.980
instead of doing it the way we have now, is if

00:00:41.980 --> 00:00:43.870
you take that Ticket Type field, just grab it from the

00:00:43.870 --> 00:00:46.790
header, and then drag it into where it says Drag Field Here.

00:00:46.790 --> 00:00:47.841
&gt;&gt; Uh-huh. Oh, cool.

00:00:47.841 --> 00:00:50.780
&gt;&gt; And so now what it's going to do, yeah. It separates all of the different

00:00:50.780 --> 00:00:55.110
ticket types to, these are all of the ones for our VIP. And then it'll give you

00:00:55.110 --> 00:00:57.620
a little subtotal for how much has been spent

00:00:57.620 --> 00:01:00.090
on VIP and then same thing for General Admission.

00:01:00.090 --> 00:01:00.500
&gt;&gt; That's really cool.

