&gt;&gt; okay, so that's pretty cool. that's summary, what were the other ones?

00:01:11.140 --> 00:01:13.690
&gt;&gt; So the other ones are matrix, which is

00:01:13.690 --> 00:01:15.980
really similar to summary, but you can also create groupings

00:01:15.980 --> 00:01:17.740
on the left-hand side. So, that's why it's a matrix,

00:01:17.740 --> 00:01:19.280
you can do it along the top and the side.

00:01:19.280 --> 00:01:19.480
&gt;&gt; Okay.

