&gt;&gt; And, then joined is kind of just a

00:01:22.510 --> 00:01:24.190
culmination of a bunch of reports that you can

00:01:24.190 --> 00:01:26.660
then just be able to show different types of

00:01:26.660 --> 00:01:29.260
data in different ways, but have one huge report.

00:01:29.260 --> 00:01:32.590
&gt;&gt; Okay, okay. So, how do we, how do we go

00:01:32.590 --> 00:01:38.339
from this summary report to that, our nice little gauge dashboard?

