you run the report, it doesn't actually save it.

00:01:45.960 --> 00:01:46.250
&gt;&gt; Okay.

00:01:46.250 --> 00:01:48.290
&gt;&gt; After it saves, click on Report.

00:01:48.290 --> 00:01:53.720
&gt;&gt; Okay, so here's our report. And we've got our VIP ticket type, total

